WEBVTT

00:03:59.026 --> 00:04:01.140
But the next time 
you look at the night sky,

00:04:01.140 --> 00:04:04.085
consider that billions of
self-replicating machines

00:04:04.085 --> 00:04:09.515
could be advancing between stars
in our galaxy right now.

00:04:09.515 --> 00:04:13.295
If they exist, one of them will eventually
land on Earth,

00:04:13.295 --> 00:04:17.115
or maybe, just maybe,
they're already here.